WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.577
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.577 --> 00:00:03.159
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.159 --> 00:00:05.964
I have some things on my heart to share with you.

00:00:06.213 --> 00:00:09.017
First off, I just want to say thank you for all your support.

00:00:09.017 --> 00:00:10.206
God bless you all.

00:00:10.206 --> 00:00:18.583
Thank you from the bottom of our hearts; we just want to say thank you for all the beautiful things that you all have said.

00:00:19.577 --> 00:00:22.720
You know, there are a lot of good emails.

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:29.180
I've had over 70,000 emails in the last week, and it's a little overwhelming for us.

00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:33.240
If I seem cranky in the comment section or anything, I apologize.

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:35.240
I have been bombarded by a lot.

00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:39.809
We're doing the best we can, but it doesn't give me the right to be cranky sometimes.

00:00:40.059 --> 00:00:42.432
I just want to say forgive me if I have been.

00:00:42.809 --> 00:00:48.018
There's a lot of the world on here, and there are a lot of people that are very hateful and very rude to us.

00:00:49.031 --> 00:00:53.760
God bless you all, the ones that are rude; we pray for you.

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:54.528
We truly do.

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:57.822
The Lord tells me, 'You've got to walk in love,' and I'm like, 'Wow.

00:00:57.822 --> 00:01:02.536
' Like I said, if they turn the channel off tomorrow, you can find me on our other YouTube channel.

00:01:06.937 --> 00:01:10.800
If you want to subscribe to that, it's Come Thrift with Me.

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:22.800
We did it because my wife likes to thrift, and we like to flip things on eBay and Poshmark and other platforms like that, like Facebook Marketplace or whatever we can do—that's how we make our living.

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:30.228
We've been doing it for like 11 years now, and God's been faithful.

00:01:30.228 --> 00:01:32.027
We've built a good business out of it.

00:01:32.213 --> 00:01:34.960
A lot of people go, 'Well, are you doing YouTube for that?

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:38.142
' No, I do YouTube because God called me to.

00:01:38.373 --> 00:01:42.400
My business and what I do for a living is Poshmark and eBay.

00:01:42.740 --> 00:01:46.110
I've been doing that for a long time, and God has been faithful.

00:01:46.110 --> 00:01:51.108
So, if you want to follow us on our Come Thrift with Me channel, it'll be a blessing.

00:01:52.788 --> 00:01:56.471
If anything happens and they shut this down—which I don't know if they will or not—but okay.

00:01:56.702 --> 00:02:00.280
First off, I just want to tell you all what happened at church on Sunday.

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:05.291
I was standing in the back like I always do, and I was praying during the service.

00:02:05.554 --> 00:02:07.245
The service was outstanding.

00:02:07.245 --> 00:02:11.600
By the way, we had a special guest speaker there: Mark Hankins was there.

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:17.880
Powerful man of God, moves in the gifts of the Spirit with signs and wonders, and it was awesome.

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:29.486
You all can go on his archives and watch the service on Sunday night and it will bless you at the Glorious Church Fellowship, I believe, YouTube channel.

00:02:29.486 --> 00:02:30.629
It might be there.

00:02:30.629 --> 00:02:33.040
You can watch it if you want to help support it.

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:35.680
It's amazing; it would bless your life.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:39.966
Mark Hankins was there Sunday morning and Sunday night.

00:02:40.263 --> 00:02:51.485
So I was standing in the back praying like I always do, and all of a sudden the Lord opened my eyes in the realm of the spirit and I saw an open heaven over that congregation.

00:02:51.908 --> 00:02:56.720
I saw the Lord Jesus sitting up there, and He was watching the service.

00:02:58.210 --> 00:03:01.360
I could see the great cloud of witnesses watching.

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:06.904
I could see them; they were peeking out over this portal over the church and they were watching.

00:03:08.624 --> 00:03:12.417
Oh my gosh, the presence of the Lord was so strong.

00:03:12.417 --> 00:03:18.263
I just sat in the back and wept because I could feel the presence of the Holy Spirit.

00:03:18.263 --> 00:03:23.760
I'm telling you, if you're dry, if you're thirsty, what a place to go.

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:29.461
Then all of a sudden, the Lord showed me a C-17.

00:03:29.461 --> 00:03:31.839
It's one of the big army planes.

00:03:31.839 --> 00:03:40.110
It's a C-17, I believe, is what it is—one of those big planes that hold all of the major military stuff.

00:03:40.540 --> 00:03:52.400
All of a sudden, that plane—I believe it's a C-17—I saw the plane swoop in and start dropping stuff out of the back of this plane in the spirit.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:58.880
Healings, anything that you've been believing for, the Lord said He's bringing it.

00:03:58.880 --> 00:04:02.947
Do not lose faith in believing for your miracle.

00:04:02.947 --> 00:04:08.130
Believe that all things are possible to him that believes.

00:04:08.130 --> 00:04:12.593
We are in the last of the last seconds before the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:14.940
People say, 'Oh, I've heard that all my life.

00:04:14.940 --> 00:04:18.823
' I'm trying to warn you that Jesus is coming.

00:04:19.154 --> 00:04:27.379
Even like people say, 'Well, you say that it's been a year or two years, whatever,' on the scope of time, we're talking thousands of years, folks.

00:04:27.379 --> 00:04:29.660
If it's 10 years, that's nothing.

00:04:29.660 --> 00:04:32.208
How fast does a year go now?

00:04:32.208 --> 00:04:34.440
It's like a snap of a finger.

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:37.759
We're already almost going into the last half of the year.

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:43.800
We have August, September, October, November, December, and then 2024 is done.

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:44.951
Look how fast.

00:04:44.951 --> 00:04:49.218
I don't know if the year went by fast for you all, but it went by very fast for me so far.

00:04:49.218 --> 00:04:54.823
So, I'm telling you, time is accelerating and we are on the verge of a major outpouring.

00:04:54.823 --> 00:04:59.509
I'm telling you, I believe with all my heart that we're going to have a great harvest of souls.

00:04:59.509 --> 00:05:04.240
I'm believing for a billion-soul harvest into the kingdom of God.

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:09.840
A great harvest of God's people coming into the kingdom.

00:05:10.496 --> 00:05:24.630
So back to the vision: I saw that big plane dropping all those packages and things that people were believing for—demonstrations and manifestations of His glory all over the people.

00:05:24.630 --> 00:05:29.989
And I'm telling you, He told me creative miracles are happening right now in this atmosphere.

00:05:29.989 --> 00:05:33.931
He said, 'Brandon, people that have autoimmune disease are being healed right now.

00:05:33.931 --> 00:05:34.550
' I could see it.

00:05:34.550 --> 00:05:39.360
And the Lord told me autoimmune disease is being healed; I saw fibromyalgia being healed last night.

00:05:40.352 --> 00:05:45.554
I want to encourage people that God is going to meet you right where you are.

00:05:45.554 --> 00:05:54.773
If you're believing for your miracle, if you're believing for a touch for your finances or whatever, I believe today is your day for your great turnaround.

00:05:54.773 --> 00:05:58.605
I believe today is your day for your miracle of your healing.

00:05:59.028 --> 00:06:09.800
If the symptoms started with pain or whatever, why can't the beginning of your miracle start with the absence of the pain, the discomfort, or the poverty being gone?

00:06:13.777 --> 00:06:17.429
It could change just like that.

00:06:17.429 --> 00:06:20.080
Just as the symptoms came on, they're gone.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:21.013
That's what's going to happen.

00:06:21.013 --> 00:06:22.776
I'm telling you, it's going to be a turnaround.

00:06:22.776 --> 00:06:28.270
And I believe with all my heart, faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:06:28.270 --> 00:06:30.469
And it's your time for your manifestation.

00:06:30.469 --> 00:06:34.960
God is no respecter of persons, and what He'll do for one, He'll do for another.

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:39.759
It just takes faith, and you just got to reach out by faith and grab on to what the Lord has for you.

00:06:42.760 --> 00:06:50.903
Number two of what I felt in my heart to tell you all: I was praying, not last night, but Saturday night.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.777
Saturday night I got a call from Chris Reed.

00:06:55.554 --> 00:07:01.600
Amazing man of God, one of the most humble people I've ever talked to on the phone.

00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:05.800
I promise y'all, and I don't say that flippantly because I'm not trying to name-drop.

00:07:08.408 --> 00:07:15.778
This guy is a genuine man of God; he loves the Lord, and it was an honor to be able to talk to somebody like him.

00:07:15.778 --> 00:07:17.804
So, I was on the phone with him and I was praying.

00:07:18.141 --> 00:07:22.240
We prayed together; he said he was praying for me and just wanted to let me know he was lifting me up in prayer.

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:28.880
Well, I got off the phone with him and I was sitting there interceding, and the Lord downloaded to me.

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:44.720
He said, 'Brandon, I want you to go back to Dana Coverstone's prophetic word—his dream that he had about the covered wagon.

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:59.520
' I went back and listened to it immediately when the Lord spoke to me, and I started listening to everything he was saying in that dream about the covered wagon, the rocking of it, and Kamala Harris on the wagon and Joe Biden being on the donkey behind her.

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:02.399
They were hitting the donkey and Joe Biden fell off.

00:08:03.679 --> 00:08:08.039
It didn't make it sound like he went home; the way it sounded to me was...

00:08:08.619 --> 00:08:16.200
Hillary came up beside her, and she had a thing on Trump's neck with a big key on it, with mold on it and everything.

00:08:16.200 --> 00:08:22.228
Go listen to that prophetic dream; I believe that was four years off.

00:08:22.228 --> 00:08:26.080
I believe we're seeing it manifest right now.

00:08:28.410 --> 00:08:28.580
Go listen to it.

00:08:29.089 --> 00:08:35.599
It's going to freak you all out because, as I said, if it doesn't happen within that time frame, everyone says, "Oh, he's a false prophet.

00:08:36.512 --> 00:08:37.342
Dana Coverstone's weird.

00:08:37.342 --> 00:08:41.940
" No, go back and listen to it.

00:08:41.940 --> 00:08:43.543
God's timing is perfect.

00:08:44.206 --> 00:08:52.000
We all thought there were a lot of people that gave words about 2020 that said Trump was going to be in office.

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:58.427
When the Lord told me, "Brandon, he's not going to be president in 2020," I had so much hate from people.

00:08:58.427 --> 00:09:01.620
In fact, I had friends who didn't want to talk to me anymore.

00:09:01.620 --> 00:09:04.149
They got really mad at me and said, "You're missing it.

00:09:04.149 --> 00:09:05.177
You're not hearing God.

00:09:05.177 --> 00:09:15.262
" And I said, "The Lord spoke to me and told me that this is not going to manifest, that Joe Biden will run the country for the timeframe.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:24.994
" And then I saw him being removed and that Kamala Harris would step in.

00:09:24.994 --> 00:09:27.270
Some people say, "Well, he wasn't removed all the way.

00:09:27.270 --> 00:09:28.560
He's still in office.

00:09:29.400 --> 00:09:31.680
" They don't even know where he's at right now.

00:09:31.680 --> 00:09:43.999
Maybe at this time in this video, they said he falsified the signature on the document, and they underlined it, saying the signatures don't match up, saying that it's not even him that signed the piece of paper, saying that he wasn't going to run anymore.

00:09:43.999 --> 00:09:48.030
There are a lot of conspiracies out there right now.

00:09:48.030 --> 00:09:52.240
So I'm just like, what's really going on?

00:09:52.240 --> 00:10:02.844
Because I told you all, and this is what I think is interesting: I told you all to watch Michelle, to watch Gavin.

00:10:02.844 --> 00:10:04.160
I've warned you.

00:10:10.160 --> 00:10:10.373
I don't know how many times I've seen Michelle Obama and Gavin.

00:10:10.373 --> 00:10:12.008
Hillary is who I thought.

00:10:13.217 --> 00:10:17.794
I said, "I saw a woman with short, sandy blonde hair.

00:10:17.794 --> 00:10:24.648
It was right in here on her head, and the Lord blotted her face.

00:10:24.648 --> 00:10:27.067
He would not allow me to see that.

00:10:27.067 --> 00:10:27.493
" Why?

00:10:31.980 --> 00:10:32.240
I have no idea.

00:10:33.893 --> 00:10:34.097
This is what the Lord did.

00:10:51.759 --> 00:10:52.440
And I saw them hit her going beside Kamala Harris going clear up into January.

00:11:01.111 --> 00:11:01.360
So, I see in part.

00:11:01.635 --> 00:11:06.068
This is just me adding my intellect to this word right now.

00:11:06.068 --> 00:11:10.739
I told you exactly what I saw, but this is just me thinking now.

00:11:10.919 --> 00:11:12.520
Don't say, "Well, you said this.

00:11:12.520 --> 00:11:16.880
" No, just listen to me.

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:23.257
What if Kamala Harris is with Hillary?

00:11:23.257 --> 00:11:28.800
Because Hillary came out immediately with Bill and endorsed Kamala Harris.

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:35.408
Then Joe—from what I understand, people are telling me that Barack Obama said, "No, not so fast.

00:11:35.408 --> 00:11:40.773
This has to be voted on at the Democratic caucus.

00:11:45.146 --> 00:11:47.884
" Well, if she ends up taking it—if she doesn't take it and they don't get her in—is he planning to do something with Kamala?

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:52.046
Is he planning to do something with Michelle and maybe Gavin in the future?

00:12:03.164 --> 00:12:03.413
I don't know.

00:12:03.413 --> 00:12:09.097
But I've told you all I've prayed over that for over two years now, that I saw her running with Gavin.

00:12:09.097 --> 00:12:11.920
They were a force to be reckoned with.

00:12:11.920 --> 00:12:13.600
People go, "Well, it's a shoo-in.

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:14.263
" No.

00:12:14.263 --> 00:12:17.030
If Michelle and Gavin go, it is.

00:12:17.030 --> 00:12:18.880
We've got to pray.

00:12:18.880 --> 00:12:28.740
It's like some people say, "Well, we've got a little bit of victory here, and we can see the finish line.

00:12:28.740 --> 00:12:31.920
" It's like the tortoise and the hare.

00:12:37.173 --> 00:12:45.744
The hare goes, "Man, I've got this race," and he goes over there and he lays down and takes a nap because he thinks he can beat that tortoise.

00:12:46.448 --> 00:12:49.376
And the tortoise is going, "I think I can.

00:12:57.956 --> 00:12:58.231
I think I can.

00:12:58.231 --> 00:13:03.199
" He's tripping over himself and he's falling, and the hare is over there sleeping.

00:13:03.199 --> 00:13:16.480
All of a sudden, the tortoise gets ahead of the hare, and the whole story everyone knows: the tortoise wins and the hare loses because he got overconfident in his ability to win.

00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:22.435
Do not let your guard down spiritually just because you think we have won.

00:13:42.670 --> 00:13:43.040
We have got to take the enemy camp seriously.

00:13:44.411 --> 00:13:55.138
And I'm not calling the Democrats the enemy; I'm talking about the principalities and powers and the rulers over the darkness and spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:13:55.138 --> 00:13:58.240
We wrestle not against flesh and blood, ladies and gentlemen, but against those things.

00:13:58.240 --> 00:13:59.680
The Bible's told us that.

00:13:59.680 --> 00:14:05.248
So, I never label a human being as an enemy, ever.

00:14:09.013 --> 00:14:09.400
But I'm talking about the demonic forces right now.

00:14:09.400 --> 00:14:11.840
That's what I'm trying to say.

00:14:11.840 --> 00:14:15.760
Never let your guard down on your enemy, ever.

00:14:15.760 --> 00:14:17.131
That's the devil.

00:14:17.131 --> 00:14:19.920
He has a plan to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:26.016
But the Bible says that Jesus came that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:14:26.016 --> 00:14:32.594
I'm just saying a lot of the theologies line up with the dark side.

00:14:40.960 --> 00:14:41.360
And I'm not saying all the Republican side is always light, but they have a tendency to sway good.

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:46.703
Never stop and be the hare laying down so the tortoise can win.

00:14:46.703 --> 00:14:52.240
Even when we have the upper hand spiritually and we see that victory finish line, don't let your guard down.

00:15:00.656 --> 00:15:00.888
I always say—this is going to be a gross illustration—but it's like an old dead dog in the road.

00:15:06.951 --> 00:15:07.155
You keep running it over until it's a greasy spot.

00:15:07.155 --> 00:15:08.667
You've got to keep going over it.

00:15:08.667 --> 00:15:15.250
That's probably a gross illustration, but you keep hitting that devil until he's a greasy spot.

00:15:15.250 --> 00:15:19.240
Don't give up when you see the first blade of your miracle.

00:15:23.970 --> 00:15:26.800
You need the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation of the whole fruit of the corn.

00:15:26.800 --> 00:15:28.240
Do not give up on this.

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:44.126
It's time for us to put our shields up even stronger and stand up even greater than what we ever had before, believing for a turnaround of our nation, to believe for things to get better and not worse.

00:15:44.126 --> 00:15:46.000
It's time to believe even greater.

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:49.930
Put the big boys up on the front line of that football team.

00:15:49.930 --> 00:15:59.063
It's time to put the great defensive backs up there going, "Hey, we're going to stop the run, and they're not going to get the touchdown.

00:16:13.406 --> 00:16:13.703
" That's what you've got to do.

00:16:14.347 --> 00:16:22.310
I probably kicked that too much, but that's why I just feel in my spirit to tell you all it's not time to stop.

00:16:35.804 --> 00:16:36.035
It's not time to give up.

00:16:36.035 --> 00:16:37.222
It's time to press.

00:16:37.222 --> 00:16:41.312
I warned you about that.

00:16:41.312 --> 00:16:45.200
So go watch that video of that covered wagon dream that he had.

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:46.948
It will bless you.

00:16:46.948 --> 00:16:52.400
It's going to make you go, "Oh my gosh, look at where we are.

00:16:52.400 --> 00:16:56.520
" But look at what he says afterward.

00:16:56.520 --> 00:17:00.240
After the election, there was a flash.

00:17:00.960 --> 00:17:03.120
And he talked about this.

00:17:03.120 --> 00:17:09.280
He said, "I saw a flash, and everybody was dazed and confused.

00:17:09.280 --> 00:17:10.347
" He warned everybody.

00:17:10.347 --> 00:17:21.680
He said everybody was dazed and confused, and everybody was on the East Coast—they were all in like cots, and they were all trying to find shelter and food and all kinds of stuff.

00:17:21.680 --> 00:17:22.280
What happens?

00:17:22.280 --> 00:17:26.640
I'm telling you all, the Lord has warned me there's a storm coming.

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:30.879
I've told you all countless times the Lord has warned me there's a storm coming.

00:17:35.120 --> 00:17:35.300
What is Dana Coverstone?

00:17:35.300 --> 00:17:37.399
He doesn't directly say it, but he's kind of insinuating something.

00:17:39.405 --> 00:17:39.588
I saw the short-haired blonde-headed lady.

00:17:52.571 --> 00:17:53.074
So that's a little recap.

00:17:53.074 --> 00:17:57.120
I saw the short blonde-headed lady with Kamala Harris.

00:17:57.120 --> 00:18:04.400
So if we see all this stuff panning out, it looks like that vision, everything I saw again.

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:08.811
It looks like I hit it right on the head.

00:18:08.811 --> 00:18:10.136
Let's just see.

00:18:10.136 --> 00:18:12.800
We'll see how it pans out.

00:18:12.800 --> 00:18:16.676
They're all going and they're happening almost like dominoes.

00:18:16.676 --> 00:18:23.827
Everything that the Lord showed me about Joe Biden being removed, I warned you all was coming and it happened.

00:18:29.080 --> 00:18:29.370
I said he will not even be running.

00:18:29.370 --> 00:18:30.600
It will not happen.

00:18:34.347 --> 00:18:34.640
I told you this last year, 2023.

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:37.070
I warned you in September of 2023.

00:18:50.769 --> 00:18:52.690
I told you this was coming.

00:18:52.690 --> 00:18:54.746
I thought it was coming in November of 2023.

00:18:54.746 --> 00:19:00.969
So, I was seeing in the future what the Lord was telling me was coming, but I thought that it was coming that year.

00:19:00.969 --> 00:19:06.799
But no, it's almost a whole year later from what I saw in the spirit.

00:19:06.799 --> 00:19:08.628
I thought this was imminent.

00:19:08.628 --> 00:19:14.046
That's why I thought it was imminent; I felt it inside.

00:19:30.479 --> 00:19:30.879
This is what's going to happen this month, this next month.

00:19:30.879 --> 00:19:37.900
I even told my son, "We're going to have an October surprise.

00:19:37.900 --> 00:19:41.627
" Well, we did have an October surprise for Israel.

00:19:47.093 --> 00:19:47.360
It was what the Lord was showing me.

00:19:47.360 --> 00:19:55.520
I prayed over it and the Lord told me there's going to be a serious event take place.

00:19:55.520 --> 00:20:03.360
I thought it was about America, but I was interceding for Israel and what happened on the Sabbath.

00:20:16.160 --> 00:20:16.570
It was a tragic thing that happened for all those people that were dragged and murdered and everything.

00:20:16.570 --> 00:20:18.210
It was terrible.

00:20:18.210 --> 00:20:20.400
I was interceding for that.

00:20:28.027 --> 00:20:28.360
But like I said, it's growing in your gifting; it's growing in what God's called you to do.

00:20:28.360 --> 00:20:29.660
I'm not perfect.

00:20:29.660 --> 00:20:31.760
I'm learning just like you all.

00:20:31.760 --> 00:20:37.760
I'm learning how to flow in the gift that God has given me.

